name: Detox Clarifying Facial Wash
ingredients:
Lactic Acid: this multi-faceted ingredient works to prevent sun damage (premature aging due to sun exposure) and exfoliates the skin to prevent the build up of impurities and oily skin breakouts.  
Glycolic Acid: part of the aha (alpha hydroxy acids) derived from cane sugar, it has the smallest molecule within the aha group so is able to penetrate skin deeply to dissolve and exfoliate sebum and other substances that bind skin cells together that cause breakouts, fine lines, acne, blackheads, dullness and oiliness.  
Detox Complex: made up of a proprietary blend containing white horehound, acai palm extract, date palm, and gotu kola the detox complex boosts the skin's self defensive system and works together to protects skin against environmental stress. this powerful combination of ingredients provides detoxifying, anti-pollution, anti-irritant properties and protects against free radical damage which can result in premature aging.

name: Detox Clarifying Facial Wash
ingredients:
Lactic Acid: this multi-faceted ingredient works to prevent sun damage (premature aging due to sun exposure) and exfoliates the skin to prevent the build up of impurities and oily skin breakouts.  
Glycolic Acid: part of the aha (alpha hydroxy acids) derived from cane sugar, it has the smallest molecule within the aha group so is able to penetrate skin deeply to dissolve and exfoliate sebum and other substances that bind skin cells together that cause breakouts, fine lines, acne, blackheads, dullness and oiliness.  
Detox Complex: made up of a proprietary blend containing white horehound, acai palm extract, date palm, and gotu kola the detox complex boosts the skin's self defensive system and works together to protects skin against environmental stress. this powerful combination of ingredients provides detoxifying, anti-pollution, anti-irritant properties and protects against free radical damage which can result in premature aging.
